(99, 97, '20140520075441139', 'Book a rewarding summer holiday!', 'This summer, unearth new cultures, seek out thrilling adventures or find a tranquil haven. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Choose from the wide range of travel packages to suit your budget with Regency Travel &amp;amp; Tours and enjoy &lt;strong&gt;Double Air Miles&lt;/strong&gt; on your travel booking.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; That’s not all, get&lt;strong&gt; QR 200 Qatar Duty Free vouchers&lt;/strong&gt; on booking any &lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-pdf/Luxury-Packages.pdf&quot;&gt;luxury travel packages&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;QR 100 Qatar Duty Free voucher&lt;/strong&gt; when booking &lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-pdf/Standard-Packages.pdf&quot;&gt;standard travel packages&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Offer valid till 30th June, 2014.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.airmilesme.com/en-qa/partner/collect/places-to-collect/regency-travel-tours.html&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20140416102042105.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;109&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;', 0, '', '', 'RTT', '', '', '', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2014-05-20 07:57:49'),
