(102, 100, '20140522073103141', 'Send a rewarding box back home with Skycom!', '&lt;p&gt;Skycom express courier service will make it easy and rewarding to send shipments back home. As an Air Miles member, enjoy:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;• an amazing &lt;strong&gt;20% OFF&lt;/strong&gt; your total bill;&lt;br /&gt;• and collect &lt;strong&gt;5 times &lt;/strong&gt;the Air Miles on all your spend&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Prompt deliveries, impeccable service, uncompromising commitment and now a more rewarding one. Plus, keep a watch on our &lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/AirMilesME?ref=hl&quot;&gt;facebook page&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;WIN&lt;/strong&gt; prizes like a shipment back home, 30,000 Air Miles and much more!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Offer valid until 26th July, 2014. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.airmilesme.com/en-bh/partner/collect/places-to-collect/skycom-1.html&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20140416102042105.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;109&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 0, '', '&lt;a style=&quot;color:#900;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com.s3.amazonaws.com/am/tnc/20140518090744137.html&quot;&gt;Terms and conditions apply&lt;/a&gt;', 'SCO', '', '', '', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2014-05-22 08:55:01'),
