(105, 103, '20140603073224153', 'Sharaf DG is now closer to you!', 'Your one-stop destination for all technology needs is now closer to you, you can now shop for all your gadgets, home appliances, smart phones and latest electronics at your nearest Union Coop outlets:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Locations: &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\n&lt;ul class=&quot;ul&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;Muhaisinah&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Al Twar&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Rashidiya&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Al Barsha&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Al Wasl&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\nRemember, use your Air Miles Card to collect Air Miles on all your spend. Plus, stretch your shopping budget further by redeeming 14,000 Air Miles for AED 100 off your purchase in-store instantly. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/sharaf-dg.html?page=1&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/Find-04.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;96&quot; height=&quot;25&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;', 0, '', '', 'SDG', '', '', '', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2014-06-09 09:53:01'),
(106, 104, '20140604115038154', 'Ramadan Offers at Sharaf DG!', '&lt;p&gt;This Ramadan, whether it&#039;s gifts or new home electronics Sharaf DG has it all and more. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Including &lt;strong&gt;travel vouchers&lt;/strong&gt; worth QR 500, &lt;strong&gt;bundle offers,&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;electronic gifts&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Air Miles&lt;/strong&gt;, Sharaf DG is your rewarding electronics destination. &lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-pdf/SDG%20Catalogue.pdf%20&quot;&gt;here &lt;/a&gt;to view their latest offers. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.airmilesme.com/en-qa/partner/collect/places-to-collect/sharaf-dg.html&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20140416102042105.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;99&quot; height=&quot;22&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 0, '', '', 'SDG', '', '', '', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2014-06-12 07:13:31'),
(107, 105, '20140608094249158', 'Travel the world with SNTTA Holidays! ', 'From breathtaking natural beauty to ancient cultures and bustling cities, the world is waiting to be explored. SNTTA Holidays wants you to book a summer vacation to remember that&#039;s why they are offering: \n&lt;ul class=&quot;ul&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Double Air Miles&lt;/strong&gt; and;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Free Delsey cabin trolley bag&lt;/strong&gt; on any package above AED 15,000 &lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\nFind a package that fits your budget and unwind somewhere different this summer. Call your nearest participating SNTTA office to, book your holidays today! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;padding-left:5px;padding-top:3%;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;table style=&quot;height:40px;width:90%;float:left;border:1px solid #000;color:#444444;font-size:12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;433&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-bottom:1px solid #000;border-right:1px solid #000;width:50%;color:#444444;font-size:12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Garhoud:&lt;/strong&gt; 04-2829000&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td style=&quot;border-bottom:1px solid #000;width:50%;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dubai Marina:&lt;/strong&gt; 04-4341644&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-right:1px solid #000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sharjah:&lt;/strong&gt; 06-5684411 &lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Abu Dhabi:&lt;/strong&gt; 02-6436525&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;bit.ly/1p8I80U%20&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/Find-04.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;92&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;', 0, '', '&lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:no