(108, 106, '20140609060846159', 'Summer escapes with Rotana!', '&lt;p&gt;Start summer right by unwinding and make the most of your weekends. Book and enjoy a weekend or weekday break at one of Rotana properties in the region to receive:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul class=&quot;ul&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;Room rates from &lt;strong&gt;just US $69 per night&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complimentary &lt;/strong&gt;breakfast&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20% discount&lt;/strong&gt; on all other services (during your stay)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free&lt;/strong&gt; wi-fi and;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;collect&lt;strong&gt; Air Miles&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make the most of this offer, book your summer escape before 15th September, 2014. For reservations or more information, click &lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://roho.it/qsffr&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;, or call &lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/rotana-hotels.html&quot;&gt;Rotana properties&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://roho.it/qsffr&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20140609061904159.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;86&quot; height=&quot;27&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 0, '', '&lt;a style=&quot;color:#900;text-decoration:none;&quot; href=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com.s3.amazonaws.com/am/tnc/20140609061021159.html&quot;&gt;Terms and conditions apply&lt;/a&gt;', 'RTH', '', '', '', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2014-06-17 09:08:52'),
