(151, 152, '20140911075730253', 'Experience an evening of exclusivity', 'Damas personally invites you to discover the creations and creativity behind one of Italy’s most loved brands.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;A VIP treatment with an exclusive offer and opportunity to meet the creator,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mr. Pasqualc Bruni&lt;/strong&gt; and be one of the first to view the exclusive high end jewellery collection being launched in Dubai.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 17th September, 2014&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time:&lt;/strong&gt; 6pm-9pm&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Venue:&lt;/strong&gt; Damas Boutique, Ground Floor, The Dubai Mall&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;To reserve your place for this exclusive event; RSVP by &lt;strong&gt;16th September, 2014&lt;/strong&gt;. This event is by invitation only.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;table style=&quot;height:21px;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;306&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;78&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:customer@damasjewellery.com?subject=Damas%20Invite&amp;amp;body=I%20(Name)%20will%20be%20attending%20the%20event%20with%20(Number)%20persons.&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;&quot; src=&quot;http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20140911084937253.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;70&quot; height=&quot;20&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td valign=&quot;middle&quot; width=&quot;219&quot;&gt; &lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div&gt; See you there!&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;', 0, '', '', 'DMS', '', '', '', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2014-09-14 09:16:07'),
