ditions, fee and charges apply<br /><br />', 'HSB', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-07-02 07:27:49'),
(221, 222, '20150521095139140', 'Look your selfie-best', '<p>Have a picture perfect summer with the hottest in eyewear from Al Jaber Optical and earn Bonus Air Miles.</p>\n<p>Get your hands on some fabulous sunglasses, branded optical frames or contact lenses from Al Jaber Optical and earn <strong>5,000 Bonus Air Miles </strong>on your first transaction.<br /><br />To top it off, Al Jaber Optical is slashing <strong>30% to 50%</strong> off all their products<strong>*</strong> until <strong>7th July 2015</strong>.<br /><br /> <a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/al-jaber-optical-center.html"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20141214142503347.png" alt="" width="100" height="21" border="0" /></a></p>', 0, '', '*Discounts are valid across Al Jaber Optical Dubai outlets only, and the Bonus Air Miles offer is valid across all Al Jaber Optical outlets in the UAE.', 'ALO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-05-26 08:24:31'),
(222, 223, '20150527130500146', 'More fun at KidZania for less..', '<p>What could be better than spending a fun day at KidZania? Spend less on your entry tickets this June with Air Miles.</p>\n<p>Get <strong>20% off</strong> when you buy KidZania tickets for both children and adults this June. Simply present your:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Air Miles Card</strong> and;</li>\n<li><strong>A valid Emirates ID</strong> at the KidZania counter to pick up the tickets.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Treat your kids to an awesome adventure with KidZania and Air Miles.<br /><br /><br /></p>', 0, '', 'Offer valid until 30th June 2015', 'AM3', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-05-31 11:12:34'),
(223, 224, '20150531155254150', 'More fun at KidZania for less..', '<p>What could be better than spending a fun day at KidZania? KidZania is a realistic educational environment that allows kids between the ages of 4 to 16 years old to do what comes naturally to them &ndash; role playing by mimicking activities done by adults in real life located at the <strong>Dubai Mall</strong>.</p>\n<p>During the month of June, spend less on your entry tickets with <br />Air Miles. Get <strong>20% off</strong> when you buy KidZania tickets for both children and adults.</p>\n<p>Simply present your:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Air Miles Card</strong> and;</li>\n<li>A<strong> valid Emirates ID</strong> at the KidZania counter located at the Dubai Mall to pick up the tickets.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Treat your kids to an awesome adventure with KidZania and Air Miles.<br /><br /><a href="https://tickets.kidzania.ae/"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150414145359103.png" alt="" width="100" height="23" border="0" /></a></p>', 0, '', 'Offer valid until 30th June 2015', 'AM3', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-06-01 08:17:17'),
(224, 225, '20150615113508165', 'Don''t miss out on Bonus Air Miles', '<p>Apply for a liquor licence or make your first transaction at African + Eastern before the month ends to enjoy 5,000 Bonus Air Miles.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.africaneastern.com/t-applylicensedubai.aspx" target="_blank">Apply online</a> today for a hassle free experience with African + Eastern. If you already have a liquor licence, head over to an African + Eastern outlet <a href="http://airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/a-e.html" target="_blank">near you </a>and you&rsquo;ll be rewarded for your first purchase.</p>\n<p>Call African + Eastern at 800-CHEERS for more information or simply visit <a href="http://www.africaneastern.com" target="_blank">www.africaneastern.com</a></p>\n<p>Offer valid until <strong>30th June 2015</strong>.<br /> <br /><a href="http://www.africaneastern.com/t-applylicensedubai.aspx" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150517130618136.png" alt="" width="106" height="25" /><br /></a></p>', 0, '', '', 'AE', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-06-15 12:25:24'),
(225, 226, '20150621123941171', 'Earn great rewards. Give to a great cause.', '<p>During Ramadan, every time you use your Air Miles Card, we will donate <strong>5%</strong> of all Air Miles earned to <strong>The Emirates Red Crescent Society</strong>.<br /><br />We&rsquo;re proud to support this UAE charity, which works tirelessly to save lives and provide care for those in need - wherever they may be.</p>\n<p>Showing your own generosity couldn&rsquo;t be simpler - just swipe your card and we will handle the rest.</p>\n<p>Plus, see where you can collect <strong>Bonus Air Miles</strong> this Ramadan!</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/offer/offers/this-ramadan-be-good-to-yourself-and-we-will-be-good-to-others.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150623133042173.jpg" alt="" width="439" height="139" border="0" /></a>Ramadan Kareem,</p>\n<p>The Air Miles Team</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/offer/offers/this-ramadan-be-good-to-yourself-and-we-will-be-good-to-others.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150414145359103.png" alt="" width="101" height="25" border="0" /></a><strong><br /></strong></p>', 0, '', '<a href="http://enews.airmilesme.com.s3.amazonaws.com/am/tnc/20150621123452171.html" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions apply.</a>', 'HSB', 'SPN', 'BSP', 'ALO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-06-23 09:31:30'),
(226, 227, '20150621170026171', 'Get Guaranteed 500 Bonus Air Miles', '<p>Simply download the new Sharaf DG mobile application before the <strong>7th of July</strong> and register your Air Miles Card to get guaranteed 500 Bonus Air Miles.</p>\n<p>What&rsquo;s more, you also enter a draw to be one of 100 lucky members to win <strong>14,000 additional Air Miles.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Here&rsquo;s what you need to do: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Click the below <strong>icons</strong> to download the Sharaf DG app</li>\n<li>Then go to <strong>Options tab</strong>, click on Profile and sign up</li>\n<li>Enter the verification <strong>code</strong> sent to your email into the app</li>\n<li>Sign in again and click Profile to enter in your<strong> Air Miles Card number </strong>to get the<strong> 500 Bonus Air Miles</strong></li>\n<li>Enjoy your Bonus Air Miles and your <strong>entry into the</strong> <strong>draw</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<table width="219">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.norq.shopex.sharaf" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150623135103173.jpg" alt="" width="118" height="41" border="0" /></a></div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/tc/app/sharaf-dg/id834006624?mt=8" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150623135011173.jpg" alt="" width="118" height="41" border="0" /></a></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Plus; This Ramadan be good to yourself, every time you use your Air Miles Card, we will donate <strong>5%</strong> of all Air Miles earned to <strong>The Emirates Red Crescent Society</strong>.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/offer/offers/this-ramadan-be-good-to-yourself-and-we-will-be-good-to-others.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150414145359103.png" alt="" width="101" height="25" border="0" /></a></p>', 0, '', '<a href="http://enews.airm