(235, 236, '20150727103713207', 'We missed you these past few months...', '<p><strong>We&rsquo;ve got a great offer* just for you:<br /></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Get <strong>1000 Bonus Air Miles</strong> when you swipe your Air Miles card at any of our <a href="http://airmilesme.com/en-ae/section/collect">partners</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Make your everyday shopping back in free massages, vouchers, phones or even free flights when you shop at our wide range of partners.</p>\n<p>Moreover, when you use your HSBC Credit Card and your Air Miles Card simultaneously, you earn Air Miles <strong>TWICE</strong>.</p>\n<p><em>*You will need to click the below button to participate in this offer. This offer is only valid until [variable field 45 days from send date].</em></p>\n<p><a href="http://t2.airmilesme.com/en-ae/article/about-us/thank-you.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20150810134519221.png" alt="" width="134" height="36" border="0" /><br /></a></p>', 0, '', '', 'SPN', 'SDG', 'LMP', 'ZCH', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', 'OOO', '2015-08-19 08:57:28'),
