(281, 282, '20151027100955299', '', 'If you live for the long weekends, what could be better than pack your bags and travel to some exotic destination this November?<br /><br />Book a holiday package to <strong>Sri Lanka</strong>, <strong>Kenya</strong> or <strong>Georgia </strong>with Al Rostamani Travel for the upcoming long weekend and collect <strong>Triple Air Miles.<br /><br /></strong>Packages start from <strong>26th</strong> or <strong>27th November</strong> to <strong>1st December </strong>2015 and include direct flights, accommodation in 4* and 5* hotels, sightseeing with entrance fees and more...<br /><br />Book now, limited seats available.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.alrostamanitravel.ae/Pages/campaign.aspx?MS=Email" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20151027153858299.png" alt="" width="152" height="34" border="0" /></a>', 0, '', 'Terms and Conditions apply. Member will be re-directed to a third party website for the holiday package inquiry', 'HSB', 'SPN', 'SDG', 'DMS', 'BSP', 'CHL', 'ADD', 'TTS', '2015-11-01 11:29:10'),
