(312, 313, '201601031426322', 'Score a DSF hat trick with Sharaf DG', 'Kick start 2016 with not one but three rewarding offers when you shop at Sharaf DG this DSF.<br /><br />Simply spend AED 3,000 or more at Sharaf DG this DSF and earn <strong>Double Air Miles*</strong> on your purchase, <strong>20% off</strong> your next two rides with <strong>Careem</strong> and <strong>Double Air Miles</strong> on your next holiday booking through <strong>Agoda</strong>. <br /><br />Make this year a rewarding one with Sharaf DG and Air Miles until <strong>1st February, 2016</strong>. <br /><br />', 0, '', '<a href="http://enews.airmilesme.com.s3.amazonaws.com/am/tnc/201601031433242.html" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions apply</a>', 'HSB', 'SPN', 'CAR', 'AGO', 'DMS', 'LMP', 'HLM', 'TTS', '2016-01-14 11:58:07'),
