(321, 322, '2016012513014224', '', '<p>Apply for a <strong>HSBC Personal Loan</strong> and unlock a world of opportunities to help realise your ambitions, no matter how big or small. Get the support you need and the bonus you deserve with HSBC and Air Miles.<br /><br />You get <strong>25,000 Bonus Air Miles</strong> with a HSBC Personal Loan of QAR 50,000 or more and a great rate starting from <strong>4.99% per annum</strong> on your HSBC Personal Loan, plus:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rates starting from 4.99% p.a.</li>\n<li>No credit life insurance fees</li>\n</ul>\nWhat can <strong>25,000 Air Miles </strong>get you?<br /><br /><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/2016021609380546.png" alt="Air Miles " width="457" height="125" border="0" /><br />\n<p>Call 800 1005 now to find out how much you could borrow<sup>1</sup>. <br /><br /></p>\n<a href="http://www.hsbc.com.qa/1/2/qa/personal/borrowing/loans/personal-loans-application-form" target="_blank"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/2016011816062617.png" alt="" width="88" height="32" border="0" /></a>', 0, '', 'Offer valid until 31st March&nbsp;2016.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.hsbc.com.qa/1/PA_esf-ca-app-content/content/pws/qa/qatar-pws/pdf/en/big-start-qatar.pdf">Terms and conditions apply.<br /></a><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;Subject to satisfactory verification and documentation.', 'FFC', 'SDG', 'DMS', 'TCB', 'MAT', 'AL2', 'HLM', 'SPC', '2016-02-16 05:39:18'),
(322, 323, '2016012815115327', '', '<p>Air Miles are delighted to bring you a fantastic promotion together with Atlantis, The Palm to ensure that 2016 is full of amazing memories.<br /><br />Book now and enjoy incredible savings on this limited <strong>Atlantis Leap Year Sale</strong>. As an Air Miles member you will receive:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>3 Air Miles</strong> for every 1USD spent on your accommodation</li>\n<li>Up to <strong>30% off</strong> Best Available Rate on all room types, with prices starting from AED 995* for stays up to 7 January 2017</li>\n<li>Free and unlimited access to <strong>Aquaventure Waterpark</strong>, with record-breaking rides and slides</li>\n<li>Free and unlimited access to <strong>The Lost Chambers Aquarium</strong>, with over 65,000 marine animals</li>\n<li>Preferential rates to swim with dolphins at<strong> Dolphin Bay</strong> and meet sea lions at<strong> Sea Lion Point</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>This offer is available for <strong>5 days only</strong>, clear the diary and book your family&rsquo;s special holiday now. The Atlantis Leap Year Sale starts today, don&rsquo;t miss out!<br /><br /><a href="https://www.atlantisthepalm.com/special-offers/air-miles"><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/2016012815471927.png" alt="" width="137" height="36" border="0" /></a></p>', 0, '', '<h5>*Terms and Conditions apply. All room rates are subject to 10% Service Charge and 10% Dubai Municipality Fee. A Tourism Dirham Fee of AED 20 per bedroom per night is applicable. Black-out dates and minimum night length of stay may apply. Air Miles members must present their Air Miles card and original Air Miles statement as proof of identification upon check-in.&nbsp;<br />Click <a href="https://www.atlantisthepalm.com/special-offers/air-miles">here</a>&nbsp;for full terms and conditions</h5>', 'HSB', 'SPN', 'DMS', 'SDG', 'TTS', 'LMP', 'ARB', 'ADD', '2016-01-31 09:53:40'),
