(325, 326, '2016020113553931', '', '<p>Enjoy extraordinary savings at the <strong>Jewellery Vault by Damas.</strong><br /><br />As one of our most valued customer, you are invited to avail exclusive offers on Diamond, Pearl, International brand Jewellery &amp; watches from The Jewellery Vault by damas.</p>\n<p>We invite you to a world of rewarding experience and timeless beauty with Damas and enjoy a day filled with exquisite pieces of fine crafted jewellery along with the must have classic accessories and get:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>60% off</strong> Diamond &amp; Pearl Jewellery</li>\n<li><strong>60% to 80% of</strong>f Watches</li>\n<li>Don&rsquo;t forget you can use your Air Miles at the Vault</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Date &amp; Time:</strong> 4th to 13th February, 10:00am - 8:00pm<br /><strong>Venue</strong>: Jumeirah Lake towers<strong>, </strong>click <strong><a href="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/2016020114052531.jpg" target="_blank">here</a> </strong>to view the map<br /><br />Don&rsquo;t miss out on this special offer &ndash; just for you.</p>', 0, '', '', 'HSB', 'DMS', 'SDG', 'SPN', 'LMP', 'ALO', 'ALR', 'ADD', '2016-02-01 10:07:15'),
