(381, 382, '', '', '<p>You can now collect Air Miles at three exciting dining venues around Dubai, offering you a variety of mouth-watering meals and delicious desserts.</p>\n<p>Experience the epitome of stylish dining at <strong>Harper&rsquo;s Bazaar Caf&eacute;</strong>, designed to be a living embodiment of the iconic fashion magazine. Tantalise your taste buds at <strong>Vicolo</strong>, the authentic Italian restaurant with a modern twist. Surrender to a sweet temptation at <strong>Morelli&rsquo;s Gelato</strong>, serving irresistible treats such as 100% Italian ice cream, milkshakes and waffles. <br /><br />What&rsquo;s more, you can redeem your Air Miles in their restaurants or on the Air Miles website for <strong>e-vouchers</strong> that can be used against your bill &ndash; you can even gift an e-voucher for that next special occasion. <br /><br />Watch out for more announcements from the Marka Group, bringing you over 50 new outlets from which to collect and spend your Air Miles.<br /><br /><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20160809142445221.png" alt="" width="168" height="47" border="0" /></p>', 6, '', '', 'HSB', 'DMS', 'SDG', 'ADD', 'BOK', 'AGD', 'TTS', 'RCZ', '2016-08-22 12:30:33'),
