(751, 752, '', '', '<p><strong>Air Miles Middle East</strong> knows how hectic life can get and running errands around the city can be both time consuming and near impossible, at the best of times. That&rsquo;s why we have partnered with <strong>Fetchr</strong>, who make picking up and dropping off parcels easier than ever. <br /><br />You can now earn <strong>16 Air Miles</strong> <strong>per AED 1 spent</strong> as well as spend your <strong>Air Miles</strong> on a <strong>Fetchr</strong> service until <strong>31st October 2017</strong>. <strong>Fetchr</strong> features their very own app that eliminates the hassle of sending and receiving packages by simply using your phone as your physical address. With the ever-growing, ever-changing cities of U.A.E., you will never have to worry about a location&rsquo;s address ever again - whenever and wherever, <strong>Fetchr </strong>will deliver what you need, when you need it. <br /><br /><strong>Here&rsquo;s how it works:<br /><br /><a title="Fetchr website" href="https://fetchr.us/"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20170803140642214.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="104" border="0" /></a><br /></strong></p>\n<p>Use your <strong>HSBC credit card</strong> to make your purchase on the <strong>Fetchr</strong> app and earn up to<strong> 17 Air Miles</strong> <strong>per AED 1 spent</strong>, getting you to rewards quicker. <strong>Air Miles</strong> gives you access to exclusive rewards including flights, hotels and shopping.</p>\nSo the next time you need to drop something off or get something for yourself, let <strong>Air Miles</strong> and <strong>Fetchr</strong> get it for you and your next drop off could be at the airport, where you whisk yourself away to your dream destination. <br /><br />Let <strong>Fetchr</strong> get that for you.<br /><br /><a title="Book your service now" href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/fetchr.html"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20170803140657214.jpg" alt="" width="190" height="41" border="0" /><br /></a>\n<h5>Offer valid until 31st October 2017. Visit <a href="https://fetchr.us/">fetchr.us</a> for further details on their services.</h5>', 6, '', '', 'HSB', 'SPN', 'DMS', 'SDG', 'BOK', 'AGD', 'TTS', 'REN', '2017-08-03 10:07:30');
