(753, 754, '', '', 'Welcome to <strong>Air Miles</strong>, the most exciting loyalty programme in the region. Congratulations on earning Air Miles for the first time - your Air Miles membership number is <strong>[EMV FIELD]CARDNUMBER[EMV /FIELD].</strong> Air Miles gives you access to exclusive rewards including flights, hotels and e-vouchers or m-vouchers to use against your everyday shopping. <br><br>That means every time you collect Air Miles at <strong><a href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/idd.html" target="_blank">IDdesign</a>, <a href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/chattels--more.html" target="_blank">Chattels</a></strong><a href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/chattels--more.html" target="_blank"> <strong>& More</strong></a>, <strong><a href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/kare-dubai.html" target="_blank">KARE design</a></strong> or any other <strong><a href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collect" target="_blank">Air Miles partner</a></strong>, you are one step closer to earning an experience you will love. So the next time you shop for furniture at <strong>IDdesign</strong> or <strong>Chattels & More</strong>, you can use your Air Miles against your total bill. <br><br>If you have forgotten to verify your email, please check your inbox and click on the verification link. <br> <br>Once you have validated your account, download the <strong><a href="https://apps.airmilesme.com/mobile" target="_blank">Air Miles mobile app</a></strong> and log in to using your email address and new password. The app will give you access to your Air Miles virtual card, easily track your Air Miles balance, redeem rewards and access great deals refreshed every Monday. <br><br>', 6, '', '', 'HSB', 'IDD', 'CHA', 'SDG', 'DMS', 'BOK', 'ADD', 'TTS', '2018-02-01 06:47:06'),
