(850, 851, '', '', 'Your <strong>September e-statement</strong> is now ready to view online. Access your e-statement now and check your monthly activity by clicking <strong><a href="https://www.airmilesme.com/en-[EMV FIELD]MORE1[EMV /FIELD]/myaccount?redirect" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong> Don''t forget to protect your account by <strong>regularly updating your password</strong>. <br><br>To celebrate the festive season of Diwali as well as the start of the cooler months, Air Miles has some exciting offers and new partners for you to enjoy.', 0, '|Air Miles has partnered with <strong>Dubai Properties</strong> to help you find your next home. You now can earn Air Miles when you buy a property. For example, when you buy a property worth AED 1 million, you would earn up to <strong>One Million Air Miles</strong>*. <em><a href="http://enews.airmilesme.com.s3.amazonaws.com/am/tnc/20170828121251239.html" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions apply</a></em>.##20171016142522288##1##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/dubai-properties.html|This Diwali season, shop for exquisite gold jewellery at&nbsp;<strong>Damas</strong>&nbsp;and enjoy free gifts. Enjoy <strong>Buy One Get One Free</strong> offers on select diamond jewellery, pearl jewellery and branded watches until 4th November. You can also earn <strong>1,000 Bonus Air Miles</strong> on any purchase of AED 3,000 and above until 19th October.##20171016142829288##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/offers/damas-diwali-offer.html|Pamper yourself with a wide range of award-winning spa treatments at <strong>Dreamworks&nbsp;Spa</strong> and earn <strong>15 Air Miles</strong> for every Dirham spent when booking online. Tranquility awaits you with state of the art facials, body scrubs and traditional Hamman rituals. Don''t forget to enter your Air Miles number at the time of check out.##20171016135134288##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/leisure-and-wellbeing/dreamworks-spa.html|<strong>Sprii.com</strong> is the&nbsp;number one shopping destination for mums in the Middle East. Earn <strong>4 Air Miles</strong> for every AED 1 spent on your purchases and enter your Air Miles number at the time of checkout.##20171016142830288##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/shopping/sprii.com.html|Get a home makeover with <strong>IDdesign</strong> - shop for stylish furniture and&nbsp;elegant accessories for your home this season and earn 4 Air Miles for every&nbsp;AED 1&nbsp; spent on your purchases at the time of check out.##20171017121438289##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/home-and-services/idd.html|Get motivated to move and live a healthier life. The Gear Sport tracks your fitness, diet and keeping you on the right path to reach your goals.&nbsp;<a href="https://uae.sharafdg.com/gear-sport/" target="_blank">Pre-order</a> now at <strong>Sharaf DG</strong>.##20171017121439289##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/shopping/sharaf-dg-electronics.html|<strong>The Toy Store</strong> offers&nbsp;a wide range of toys for children of all ages. So head over&nbsp;and buy the perfect game or toy and earn <strong>1 Air Mile</strong> for every Dirham spent.##20171016141905288##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/shopping/the-toy-store.html|Earn <strong>3 Air Miles</strong> for every Dirham spent at <strong>Chili''s</strong>. Enjoy great quality American food at Chili''s as well as great service across all of its friendly and family fun restaurants.##20171016141906288##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/dining/chilis.html|<strong>Al Jaber Optical</strong>&nbsp;offers customers&nbsp;a wide range of trendy eyewear products designed with the fashion-conscious customer in mind. Earn 1 Air Mile for every Dirham spent at Al Jaber Optical.##20171016142905288##2##https://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/collectcat/shopping/al-jaber-optical.html|You can now redeem your Air Miles for an AED 100 m-voucher from <strong>Go