(941, 973, '', '', '<strong>Greetings from Air Miles<br></strong><br>We would like to extend our sincere apologies for any inconvenience you may have experienced when you redeemed for Air Miles rewards on <strong>23rd January 2018</strong>. Unfortunately, we encountered a technical issue which resulted in the e-vouchers being invalid when presented at our partner stores and the same issue applied to any m-vouchers redeemed in our mobile app. Further to checking our system, we found redemption activity from your account was made on this day. In this regard, we will process the refund of the corresponding Air Miles spent on this redemption by <strong>1st March 2018</strong>.<br><br>If you have any questions and get the details about your redemption activity, please contact our customer support team at +971 4 391 3400 (UAE), +973 1758 3888 (Bahrain), +974 4444 9210 (Qatar), Sunday to Thursday, 9:00 am to 6:00 pm.  If you have already reached out to us with regards to this matter, please disregard this message.<br><br>We are grateful for your support, and we hope you continue to enjoy the benefits of Air Miles.<br><br>Sincerely,<br><br>The Air Miles Team', 0, '', '', 'HSB', 'DMS', 'SDG', 'ADD', 'BOK', 'AGD', 'TTS', 'RCZ', '2018-02-04 10:00:57'),
