(15, 'Budget Terms & Conditions', '&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;All bookings for pick-up and drop-off in UAE are defined as Domestic bookings&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;Air Miles will be issued only on rental charges of the vehicle and not on additional charges for GPS, Baby Seats, missing fuel, Insurances, or Salik and Traffic Fines&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;Domestic UAE car rental bookings i.e. daily, weekly and monthly rentals with public rates only qualify for the collection of Air Miles&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;Air Miles accruals not permitted on promotional, discounted or contracted rates and also not applicable in conjunction with other loyalty programmes&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;Only those bookings (domestic) made via Budget UAE office, and/or Budget UAE Call Centre (Toll Free: 800 2722 or Tel: +971(0) 4 88 40022 / Fax: +971(0) 4 282 5616; reservations@budget-uae.com Open: 24 hours, 7 days a week) and/or Budget UAE Website (www.budget-uae.com) will be rewarded with Air Miles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '2014021108020841', '', '2014-02-11 13:04:33'),
(16, 'Damas terms and conditions', '&acirc;&euro;&cent; The family package is inclusive of flights, 3 nights hotel stay on half board basis, and 2-way airport transfers<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; The family package can be availed by 2 adults and 2 children (aged between 3 years and 13 years) only to Colombo city and back for a total of 3 nights stay on Half Board basis<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Unaccompanied minors (passengers below the age of 17 travelling without adults) will not be allowed<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Air Miles reserves the right to choose the airline, specific flights, hotels, room types and other associated elements of the Family Package<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; All flight tickets and hotel stays are available for utilization/travel before 31/10/2014, excluding 7 days before, including and after Eid Al Fitr &amp; Eid Al Adha<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Flights &amp; Hotel Bookings will be subject to availability<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Passports of all passengers must be at least 6 months valid in order to travel<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Flights &amp; hotel bookings are subject to seat/room availability<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Air Miles needs to be advised of your desired travel dates at least 14 working days in advance<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Air Miles will arrange the flights, airport transfers and hotel stays whilst we will not be liable for the arrangement &amp; payment of Visas, Insurance and all other travel arrangements<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Once the flight tickets and hotel bookings have been confirmed, we will not entertain refund and/or date change requests<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Following the hotel &amp; flight confirmations, any flight/hotel booking updates will not be communicated by Air Miles. The airline or travel agency will make best endeavors to communicate any updates to you, however it is the passengers ultimate responsibility to check flight timings <br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; When making a Flight Reward booking, the name(s) provided at the time of booking must be the full name of the person(s) travelling, as it appears on their passport - proof of identity will be required at check-in<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Each passenger must have a valid passport or travel document and details must be provided as part of the Flight Reward booking process<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; It is the sole responsibility of each passenger to have all appropriate travel documents required by law in their possession upon departure<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Electronic tickets will be issued and sent to the Members&acirc;&euro;&trade; registered email address <br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; We are not responsible for the fulfillment of special requests (e.g. meal choices, seat allocation, wheel chair, infant bassinet etc). The Member will need to contact the airline directly for all special requests<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; We accept no responsibility for any loss from or related to: <br />o Travel cancellation or delay<br />o Loss or damage to luggage or other property<br />o Personal accident or sickness suffered while travelling<br />o Refund charges<br />o Any other circumstances arising from Spending of Air Miles outside the control of Air Miles.<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; The airlines and other Reward suppliers providing travel or other services are independent contractors and not agents or employees of Air Miles<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; We are not liable for the acts, errors, omissions, representations, warranties, breaches or negligence of any suppliers<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; We have no liability and will make no refund in the event of any delay, cancellation, overbooking, strike, force majeure or other causes beyond suppliers&acirc;&euro;&trade; direct control <br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; It is the passengers responsibility to review any travel restrictions, warnings, announcements and advisories issued prior to Spending Air Miles for travel Rewards to international destinations <br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; By offering Flight Rewards to particular international destinations, we do not represent or warrant any travel as advisable or without risk, and as such are not liable for damages or losses that may result from travel to such destinations<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Bonus Air Miles will be credited into the respective accounts latest by 1st June, 2014<br />&acirc;&euro;&cent; Winner will be chosen by electronic ballot system at the Air Miles office Dubai on 1st June, 2014<br /><br />', '20140416134253105', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2016-05-04 06:16:53'),
