(34, 'Gift Voucher Terms and Conditions', '<ul>\n<li>\n<div>GVs WORTH 20% OF PURCHASE VALUE ABOVE AED 500 WILL BE ISSUED TO CUSTOMERS, WHICH CAN BE REDEEMED ON NEXT PURCHASE.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>GVs WILL NOT BE ISSUED ON SERVICE COST LIKE-DELIVERY/STORAGE/REPAIR CHARGES.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>CUSTOMERS CANNOT PAY FOLLOWING SERVICE COSTS BY GVs- DELIVERY/STORAGE/REPAIR CHARGES.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>NO CASH REFUND/ CREDIT NOTE/EXCHANGE CAN BE AVAILED FOR THE ORIGINAL PURCHASE OR ON THE GV REDEEMED ITEM(S).</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>GV CANNOT BE CONVERTED IN CASH OR ANY OTHER MODE.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>IN CASE OF CHEQUE PAYMENT, GV WILL BE ISSUED ONLY AFTER CLEARANCE OF CHEQUE.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>NO GV WILL BE ISSUED ON A PURCHASE MADE BY ANY OTHER NON-PEHF (NON DSF) GV &amp; CASH COMBINED.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>NO GV WILL BE ISSUED ON LPO (COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT) BILLINGS.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>GV CANNOT BE AVAILED ON AS IS ITEMS*.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>VALIDITY OF GV IS FOR 90 DAYS FROM THE DATE OF ISSUE.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>GV CANNOT BE REDEEMED DURING ANY OTHER SALE/PROMOTION.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>ORIGINAL GV SHOULD BE PRODUCED AT THE TIME OF REDEMPTION.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>IN CASE OF CANCELLATION OR MODIFICATION OF A PURCHASE TRANSACTION, THE CUSTOMER WILL HAVE TO PROVIDE PAN EMIRATES WITH THE ORIGINAL GIFT VOUCHER ISSUED AGAINST TRANSACTION. IN CASE THE GV WAS UTILIZED ON ANY SUBSEQUENT PURCHASE, THE AMOUNT WILL BE DEDUCTED FROM THE CUSTOMERS ORIGINAL TRANSACTION IF IT IS BEING CANCELLED.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>NO EXCHANGE/REFUNDS ALLOWED ON THE ORIGINAL PURCHASE OR ON THE ITEMS REDEEMED BY GIFT VOUCHER.</li>\n</ul>\n<br />GV: Gift Voucher<br /><br />PEHF: Pan Emirates Home Furnishing <br /><br />*AS IS ITEMS: Items reserved for display pieces that are sold at a bargain.<br /><br />', '2015020415505334', 'Richel', '2015-02-04 12:37:28'),
(35, 'Al Jaber Optical Terms and Conditions apply', '<ul>\n<li>Voucher redeemable on frames and sunglasses only.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Voucher is valid for 3 months from date of issue.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Prizes cannot be exchanged for cash or Air Miles.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Each gift voucher is worth AED 250 which can be redeemed at any Al Jaber Optical outlet in the UAE.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Each voucher can be used against a single transaction only. Expired vouchers will not be renewed.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Voucher cannot be used in conjunction with any other promotion and/or sales/discount offers at the time of usage.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right to change the offer and terms and conditions at any point of time without prior notice.</li>\n</ul>', '2015021611073046', 'Richel', '2015-03-03 12:34:13'),
