(37, 'Air Miles Birthday Campaign- Terms and Conditions', '1. The competition terms and conditions and all promotional materials are run by Rewards Management Middle East FZ &ndash; LLC (RMMEL) the parent company that operates the Air Miles loyalty programme. All references to Air Miles in the terms and conditions refer to the parent company.<br /> <br /> 2. The promotion period is from 16th April &ndash; 16th May, 2015 only run in the UAE.<br /> <br /> 3. Air Miles staff and immediate family members are eligible to participate in this campaign but will not enter the draw to win the grand prize.<br /> <br /> 4. Only Air Miles members residing and holding an Air Miles account in the UAE are eligible to participate.<br /><br />5. Members shopping and using their Air Miles Card at the below participating partners during the promo period will equate an entry into the raffle draw to win a share of 196,000 Air Miles. <br /><br />Participating Partners:<br />\n<ul>\n<li>Lamcy Plaza</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Arabian Centre</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Spinneys</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Sharaf DG</li>\n</ul>\n<br />6. All members with qualifying entry (ies) will be tabulated and from this pool, a random selection of winners will be drawn<br /> <br /> 7. There will be 14 winners winning 14,000 Air Miles each. The winner will be notified that he/she has won the prize by telephone by 4th June 2015. If the winner remains not contactable for a period of 30 days, the prize will be terminated<br /> <br /> 8. The winning Air Miles will be credited into the respective Air Miles account latest by 7th June, 2015.<br /><br />9. Prizes are non-transferable. There will be no cash prize alternative.<br /> <br /> 10. Air Miles will not hand over the prize until the winner has supplied documented evidence to an Air Miles Representative a valid ID copy of the winner.<br /> <br /> 11. Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify and reclaim any bonus Air Miles / prizes for any person(s) it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions.<br /> <br /> 12. These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles.<br /> <br /> 13. The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any dispute arising shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the Dubai Courts.<br /> <br /> 14. The promoter of this promotion is Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC, 2nd Floor, Building 15, Dubai Internet City, Dubai, in the United Arab Emirates.', '20150413163109102', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-04-16 07:55:13'),
(38, 'The Cellars Draw Terms and Conditions', '[1] Entrants must be over 21 years old.<br /><br />[2] Entrants should have a valid Dubai ID.<br /><br />[3] Entrants should be an Air Miles Member.<br /><br />[4] Submissions after Thursday, 21st May, 12:00 pm will not be considered.<br /><br />[5] Air Miles employees along with their immediate families are not eligible to participate in this competition.<br /><br />[6] Vouchers cannot be exchanged or withdrawn for cash.<br /><br />[7] The management reserves the right to publish the name of the winner.', '20150507141218126', 'Richel', '2015-05-07 10:13:24'),
(39, 'Al Jaber Optical 5,000 Bonus Air Miles ', '1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5,000 Bonus Air Miles shall be awarded to any member who swipes the Air Miles card for the very first time at any Al Jaber Optical outlet<br /><br />2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All consequent purchases will continue to earn Standard Air Miles <br /><br />3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Part Sale discounts are valid across Al Jaber Optical Dubai outlets only, and the Bonus Air Miles offer is valid across all Al Jaber Optical outlets in the UAE<br /><br />4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bonus Air Miles will be credited to members&rsquo; accounts two weeks after the promotion ends<br /><br />5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Air Miles and Al Jaber Optical reserve the right to change the terms of the promotion at any given time', '20150527095748146', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-05-27 05:57:48'),
