(41, 'Ramadan Terms & Conditions ', '<ul>\n<li>The campaign&nbsp;terms and conditions and all promotional materials are run by Rewards Management Middle East FZ &ndash; LLC (RMMEL) the parent company that operates the Air Miles loyalty programme. All references to Air Miles in the terms and conditions refer to the parent company.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The promotion period is from 23rd&nbsp;June &ndash; 23rd&nbsp;July 2015 only run in the UAE in affiliation with Emirates Red Crescent (Permit Number - A15099).<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Emirates Red Crescent was established on 31/01/1983 and recognized by the Islamic Affairs and Charitable Activities in Dubai (IACAD)&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles staff are eligible to participate in this campaign.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Only Air Miles members residing and holding an Air Miles account in the UAE are eligible to participate.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Members shopping and using their Air Miles Card at any Air Miles partners during the promotion period, Air Miles will donate 5% of the standard Air Miles collected and upto a total of 10 Million Air Miles to the Emirates Red Crescent Society.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The Air Miles to be contributed will be handed over to Emirates Red Crescent latest by 7th August, 2015.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles contribution to the Emirates Red Crescent Society will be in form of goods and no cash prize alternative.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles will donate to a maximum of 10 Million Air Miles at the end of the promotion.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify and reclaim any Bonus Air Miles / prizes for any person(s) it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any di