(43, 'Qatar Ramadan Terms and Conditions ', '<ol>\n<li>The campaign terms and conditions and all promotional materials are run by Rewards Management Middle East FZ &ndash; LLC (RMMEL) the parent company that operates the Air Miles loyalty programme. All references to Air Miles in the terms and conditions refer to the parent company.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The promotion period is from 2nd July&nbsp;&ndash; 16th July 2015 only run in the Qatar<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles staff are eligible to participate in this campaign only to earn Bonus Air Miles and not participate on the raffle draw.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Only Air Miles members residing and holding an Air Miles account in the Qatar&nbsp;are eligible to participate.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Members shopping for QR 450 and above and use their Air Miles Card at any Air Miles partners during the promotion period, will stand a chance to be one of lucky 20 winners winning&nbsp;250,000&nbsp;Air Miles.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Multiple&nbsp;transactions of QAR 450 will entitle the member multiple chances to enter the draw<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Members shopping and using their Air Miles Card at the following Air Miles partners are eligible to collect Double Air Miles.<br /><br />a.&nbsp;Teyseer Service Centre<br /><br />b.&nbsp;Techno Blue<br /><br />c. Al Mana Partners&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Double Air Miles will be credited into the respective Air Miles account latest by 30th August, 2015.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>All members with qualifying entry(ies) will be tabulated and from this pool, a random selection of winners will be drawn<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Each winner&nbsp;will be notified that he/she has won the prize by telephone by 30th August&nbsp;2015. If the winner remains not contactable for a period of 2 weeks, the prize will be terminated<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Prizes are non-transferable. There will be no cash prize alternative.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles will not hand over the prize until the winner has supplied documented evidence to an Air Miles Representative a valid ID copy of the winner.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify and reclaim any Bonus Air Miles / prizes for any person(s) it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any dispute arising shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the Dubai Courts.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The promoter of this promotion is Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC, 2nd Floor, Building 15, Dubai Internet City, in the United Arab Emirates.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>All members swiping their Air Miles card during the campaign period will enjoy Bonus offers as listed below.</li>\n</ol>', '20150630121929180', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-07-02 08:18:40'),
(44, 'UAE - Spend In-Store ', 'To redeem your Air Miles in-store at Sharaf DG, Lamcy Plaza, Damas,&nbsp;Arabian Center, Hallmark and The Toy Store; Present your Air Miles card along with a valid ID when you are paying for your purchases at the below&nbsp;listed partner.<br /><br />Find out your&nbsp;nearest Partner location:&nbsp;<br /><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/sharaf-dg.html" target="_blank">Sharaf DG</a><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/lamcy-plaza.html" target="_blank">Lamcy Plaza<br /></a><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/arabian-center.html" target="_blank">Arabian Center</a><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/damas.html" target="_blank">Damas</a><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/hallmark.html">Hallmark</a><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/partner/collect/places-to-collect/the-toy-store.html" target="_blank">The Toy Store</a><br /><br /><strong>Please see T&amp;C&rsquo;s below for more details.</strong><br /><br />\n<ul>\n<li>A minimum spend of AED 50 is required to redeem your Air Miles. AED 50 value is equivalent to 7,000 Air Miles and can be redeemed towards your purchase at any of the participating Partner outlets.</li>\n<li>The value of your redemptions cannot exceed the total value of your purchase.</li>\n<li>To redeem your Air Miles in-store you must present your Air Miles card and valid ID as proof of identity. Your details must be registered with Air Miles for validation purposes.</li>\n<li>Air Miles are redeemable in-store only and cannot be used to purchase goods over the phone or via the participating Partner outlets.</li>\n<li>Air Miles can be used as part payment and any balance must be paid at the time of purchase.</li>\n<li>Air Miles can be collected on the value of your redemption.</li>\n<li>Air Miles are not redeemable in conjunction with any other offer, promotion or discounted rate, unless otherwise stated.</li>\n<li>Once the redemption has been processed it cannot be cancelled or refunded.</li>\n<li>All participating Partner outlets&nbsp;reserves the right to issue credit notes redeemable in their&nbsp;outlets only in respect of items purchased using Air Miles which are subsequently returned.</li>\n<li>All participating Partner outlets&nbsp;standard terms and conditions also apply.</li>\n</ul>', '20150915153935257', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-09-17 08:24:48'),
(45, 'Qatar - Spend In -store', 'To redeem your Air Miles in-store at Sharaf DG, Damas and Family Food Centre; Present your Air Miles card along with a valid ID when you are paying for your purchases at the below listed partner.<br /><br />Find out your nearest Partner location: <br /><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-qa/partner/collect/places-to-collect/sharaf-dg.html" target="_blank">Sharaf DG</a><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-qa/partner/collect/places-to-collect/damas-2.html" target="_blank">Damas</a><br /><a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-qa/partner/collect/places-to-collect/family-food-centre.html" target="_blank">Family Food Centre</a><br /><br /><strong>Please see T&amp;C&rsquo;s below for more details.</strong><br /><br />\n<ul>\n<li>A minimum spend of QAR&nbsp;50 is required to redeem your Air Miles. QAR&nbsp;50 value is equivalent to 7,000 Air Miles and can be redeemed towards your purchase at any of the participating Partner outlets.</li>\n<li>The value of your redemptions cannot exceed the total value of your purchase.</li>\n<li>To redeem your Air Miles in-store you must present your Air Miles card and valid ID as proof of identity. Your details must be registered with Air Miles for validation purposes.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Air Miles are redeemable in-store only and cannot be used to purchase goods over the phone or via the participating Partner outlets.</li>\n<li>Air Miles can be used as part payment and any balance must be paid at the time of purchase.</li>\n<li>Air Miles can be collected on the value of your redemption.</li>\n<li>Air Miles are not redeemable in conjunction with any other offer, promotion or discounted rate, unless otherwise stated.</li>\n<li>Once the redemption has been processed it cannot be cancelled or refunded.</li>\n<li>All participating Partner outlets standard terms and conditions also apply.</li>\n</ul>', '20150915155826257', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-09-17 08:26:59'),
