(47, 'African+ Eastern In-store Redemption.', 'Enjoy instant redemptions at African+ Eastern Al Wasl and Marina Walk stores.To redeem your Air Miles in-store simply present your Air Miles card along with a valid ID when you are paying for your purchases at the below listed partner.<br /><br /><strong>Al Wasl Store:&nbsp;</strong>Al Wasl Rd., behind Spinneys Supermarket,&nbsp;Phone: +9714 394 2676<br /><br /><strong>Marina Walk Store</strong> :&nbsp;Marina&nbsp;Dubai&nbsp;Tel: +971 4 368 3981<br /><br />Please see T&amp;C&rsquo;s below for more details.<br />\n<ul>\n<li>The value of your redemptions cannot exceed the total value of your purchase.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>To redeem your Air Miles in-store you must present your Air Miles card and valid ID as proof of identity. Your details must be registered with Air Miles for validation purposes.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles are redeemable in-store at African+ Eastern only at the &nbsp;Al Wasl and Marina Walk branch and cannot be used to purchase goods over the phone.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles can be used as part payment and any balance must be paid at the time of purchase.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles can be collected on the value of your redemption.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Air Miles are not redeemable in conjunction with any other offer, promotion or discounted rate, unless otherwise stated.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Once the redemption has been processed it cannot be cancelled or refunded.</li>\n</ul>', '20150920111332262', 'Richel', '2015-09-20 07:37:20'),
