(56, 'Spend, Collect & Fly - Terms & Conditions 2015', '<ul type="disc">\n<li>The competition terms and conditions and all promotional materials are run by Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC (RMMEL) the parent company that operates the Air Miles loyalty programme. All references to Air Miles in the terms and conditions refer to the parent company</li>\n<li>The promotion period is from&nbsp;<strong>1st</strong>&nbsp;to<strong>&nbsp;31st December, 2015</strong>&nbsp;only run in UAE</li>\n<li>Air Miles staff and immediate family members are eligible to participate in this campaign to collect&nbsp;<strong>Bonus Air Miles</strong>&nbsp;and wont be entitled to enter the prize draw.</li>\n<li><strong>Two&nbsp;</strong>lucky winners will be chosen through a fair computerized draw.</li>\n<li>Each lucky winner will win two travel tickets each to a destination pre-determined as mentioned on the website and any communications received.</li>\n<li>Only Air Miles members residing and holding an Air Miles account in the UAE are eligible to participate in the draw</li>\n<li>Members shopping and using their Air Miles Card at the following Air Miles partners -&nbsp;<strong>Damas</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Al Jaber Optic</strong><strong>al</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Hallmark</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Lamcy Plaza</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Arabian</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Center&nbsp;</strong>will be issued with the respective amount of bonus Air Miles during the promotion period.</li>\n<li>Bonus Air Miles will be credited into the respective Air Miles account latest by&nbsp;<strong>7th February, 2016</strong>.</li>\n<li>All Air Miles Partners are included in this competition with no minimum spend criteria</li>\n<li>The results of the prize draw are final and no correspondence will be entered into. Prizes are non-transferable. There will be no cash prize alternative</li>\n<li>The prize featured in all printed materials and/or website is shown for illustrative purposes only.</li>\n<li>All members with qualifying entry(ies) will be tabulated and from this pool, a random selection of one lucky winner will be drawn</li>\n<li>The winner will be notified that he/she has won the prize by telephone by&nbsp;<strong>31st&nbsp;January, 2016</strong>.&nbsp;If the winner remains not contactable for a period of 6 months, the prize will be terminated</li>\n<li>Air Miles will not hand over the prize until the winner has supplied documented evidence to an Air Miles Representative a valid ID copy of the winner</li>\n<li>The winner is required to attend a prize presentation ceremony and other public programs as and when required by Air Miles at their own cost and expense.</li>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify any person it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions</li>\n<li>These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles.</li>\n<li>The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any dispute arising shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the Dubai Courts</li>\n<li>Travel to be completed before&nbsp;<strong>31st March, 2016</strong></li>\n<li>General Air Miles travel terms and conditions apply</li>\n<li>Winners will be awarded with economy class flight tickets and hotel stay but visa applications is at the sole discretion of the traveler</li>\n<li>The promoter of this promotion is Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC, 2nd Floor, Building 15, Dubai Internet City, Dubai, in the United Arab Emirates.</li>\n</ul>', '20151022123105294', 'Yohan Aluthwala', '2015-12-01 12:59:18'),
(57, 'Terms and Conditions', '<ul>\n<li>The competition terms and conditions and all promotional materials are run by Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC (RMMEL) the parent company that operates the Air Miles loyalty programme. All references to Air Miles in the terms and conditions refer to the parent company</li>\n<li>Only Air Miles members residing and holding an Air Miles account in the UAE are eligible to participate in the campaign and enter the draw</li>\n<li>Air Miles staff and immediate family members are eligible to participate in this campaign to collect Bonus Air Miles and wont be entitled to enter the prize draw</li>\n<li>Bonus Air Miles will be credited into the respective Air Miles account within 6 weeks after the camapign ends</li>\n<li>The results of the prize draw are final and no correspondence will be entered into. Prizes are non-transferable. There will be no cash prize alternative</li>\n<li>The prize featured in all printed materials and/or website is shown for illustrative purposes only</li>\n<li>All members with qualifying entry(ies) will be tabulated and from this pool, a random selection of one lucky winner will be drawn</li>\n<li>The winner will be notified that he/she has won the prize by telephone within 6 weeks after campaign ends. If the winner remains not contactable for a period of 2&nbsp;months, the prize will be terminated</li>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify any person it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions</li>\n<li>These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles</li>\n<li>The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any dispute arising shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the Dubai Courts</li>\n<li>The promoter of this promotion is Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC, 2nd Floor, Building 15, Dubai Internet City, Dubai, in the United Arab Emirates</li>\n</ul>', '20151027093901299', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-10-27 11:58:17'),
(58, 'HSBC Advance Terms & Conditions', '<ol>\n<li>Air Miles <a href="http://www.airmilesme.com/en-ae/article/general/terms-conditions.html" target="_blank">terms and conditions</a>&nbsp;apply<br /><br /></li>\n<li>HSBC Advance eligibility criteria: a) Minimum monthly average balance in deposits and/or investments of AED 100,000 (or equivalent in foreign currency) or more or b) Minimum monthly salary transferred to HSBC of AED 15,000 (or equivalent in foreign currency) or more.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Personal loan rate is based on reducing balance, which is the interest calculated on a monthly basis on the remaining principal amount. Your interest rate is based on qualifying criteria; please contact us for details of the rate that will apply to your loan.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Home loan rate is based on reducing balance and applicable to UAE resident Premier customers, borrowing a loan amount of more than AED 5 Million.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Cash advance is subject to availability of funds in your account(s) and confirmation from your country of residence. One Global Emergency Encashment per 48 hours is &nbsp;allowed.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Travel insurance is provided by Zurich Insurance Middle East S.A.L. and subject to their policy terms and conditions. HSBC is not responsible for any claims, processing or otherwise.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Valet parking is up to 4 visits per month</li>\n</ol>', '20151029150503301', 'Yohan Aluthwala', '2015-11-04 07:36:09'),
(59, 'Sharaf DG - Terms and Conditions', '&bull; Double Air Miles is valid for stays from 16th November to 16th December&nbsp;2015.<br /><br />&bull; Bonus Miles will be credited to member&rsquo;s who&rsquo;ve chosen to participate in the offer by clicking the &lsquo;click here to participate&rsquo; button. <br /><br />&bull; Bonus Miles will be credited to members&rsquo; account by the 31st of December 2015.<br /><br /> &bull; Miles are not applicable on purchases of extended warranty products, items classified as impulse purchases or services purchased.<br /><br />&bull; Not valid in conjunction with any other promotion/offer.<br /> <br /> &bull; Sharaf DG standard Terms and Conditions will apply.', '20151111154011314', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-11-15 07:37:22'),
(60, 'Qatar Festive - Terms & Conditions ', '<ul>\n<li>The competition terms and conditions and all promotional materials are run by Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC (RMMEL) the parent company that operates the Air Miles loyalty programme. All references to Air Miles in the terms and conditions refer to the parent company</li>\n<li>The promotion period is from <strong>1st to 31st December, 2015&nbsp;</strong>only run in Qatar</li>\n<li>Air Miles staff and immediate family members are eligible to participate in this campaign to collect Bonus Air Miles and wont be entitled to enter the prize draw.</li>\n<li>One lucky&nbsp;winner will be chosen through a fair computerized draw.</li>\n<li>The&nbsp;lucky winner will win <strong>500,000 Air Miles</strong> which can be redeemed against flight tickets based on the qoute attained by the flight booking system</li>\n<li>Only Air Miles members residing and holding an Air Miles account in the Qatar&nbsp;are eligible to participate in the draw</li>\n<li>Members shopping and using their Air Miles Card at participating Air Miles partners will be issued with the respective amount of bonus Air Miles during the promotion period.</li>\n<li>Bonus Air Miles will be credited into the respective Air Miles account latest by <strong>7th February, 2016</strong>.</li>\n<li>All Air Miles Partners are included in this competition with no minimum spend criteria</li>\n<li>The results of the prize draw are final and no correspondence will be entered into. Prizes are non-transferable. There will be no cash prize alternative</li>\n<li>The prize featured in all printed materials and/or website is shown for illustrative purposes only.</li>\n<li>All members with qualifying entry(ies) will be tabulated and from this pool, a random selection of one lucky winner will be drawn</li>\n<li>The winner will be notified that he/she has won the prize by telephone by <strong>31st January, 2016</strong>. If the winner remains not contactable for a period of 6 months, the prize will be terminated</li>\n<li>Air Miles will not hand over the prize until the winner has supplied documented evidence to an Air Miles Representative a valid ID copy of the winner</li>\n<li>The winner is required to attend a prize presentation ceremony and other public programs as and when required by Air Miles at their own cost and expense.</li>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify any person it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions</li>\n<li>These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles.</li>\n<li>The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any dispute arising shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the Dubai Courts</li>\n<li>General Air Miles travel terms and conditions apply</li>\n<li>The promoter of this promotion is Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC, 2nd Floor, Building 15, Dubai Internet City, Dubai, in the United Arab Emirates.</li>\n</ul>', '20151112145100315', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-11-23 11:50:21'),
