6 months, the prize will be terminated</li>\n<li>Air Miles will not hand over the prize until the winner has supplied documented evidence to an Air Miles Representative a valid ID copy of the winner</li>\n<li>The winner is required to attend a prize presentation ceremony and other public programs as and when required by Air Miles at their own cost and expense.</li>\n<li>Air Miles reserves the right at its sole discretion to disqualify any person it suspects to be acting or has acted in violation of these Terms and Conditions</li>\n<li>These Terms and Conditions are subject to change, addition, or amendment, at any time, as per the discretion of Air Miles.</li>\n<li>The Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of the UAE and any dispute arising shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the Dubai Courts</li>\n<li>General Air Miles travel terms and conditions apply</li>\n<li>The promoter of this promotion is Rewards Management Middle East FZ LLC, 2nd Floor, Building 15, Dubai Internet City, Dubai, in the United Arab Emirates.</li>\n</ul>', '20151112150031315', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2015-11-23 11:49:45'),
(62, 'Al Rostamani Travel -  Festive Packages', '<p><img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20151124162046327.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="190" border="0" /><br /><br />Whether you''re planning the holiday season with loved ones, Select from a variety of packages designed<br />especially for you by Al Rostamani Travel. To know more please call&nbsp;<strong>800-ART (800 278)</strong> and experience a magical holiday.</p>\n<p><strong>Package&nbsp;1</strong></p>\n<p><br />Maldives - 5 days<br /><br />Paradise Island Resort 5*hotel<br />Starting from AED 3,075 per person<br /><br />Package Inclusion:<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4 nights accommodation in Paradise Island hotel 5*<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Meal plan on half board basis (breakfast + 1 meal per day)<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Return speedboat transfer<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Airport assistance<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Infant (below 2 yrs) is free of charge (subject to USD 6 green tax) per night <br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All applicable taxes<br />&nbsp;<br />Important Note: Peak season supplements applicable<br /><br />Additional Compulsory Festive Supplement<br /><br />Christmas Eve dinner (24 Dec 2015): AED 285 per adult, AED 145 per child<br /><br />New Year&rsquo;s Eve dinner (31 Dec 2015): AED 525 per adult, AED 260 per child<br /><br />&nbsp;<br />Validity: 01 Dec 2015 &ndash; 22 Jan 2016<br /><br />&nbsp;<br /><strong>Package&nbsp;2</strong><br /><br />Zanzibar - 4 days<br /><br />Bluebay Beach Resort, Zanzibar 4*deluxe resort on the beach<br /><br />Starting from AED 1,930 per person<br />Package Inclusion:<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3 nights accommodation in Bluebay Beach Resort 4*<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Meal plan on half board basis (breakfast + 1 meal per day)<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Return airport transfer<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Applicable taxes<br /><br />Validity: until 22 Jan 2016</p>', '20151124134528327', 'Yohan Aluthwala', '2015-12-31 14:09:06'),
(63, 'Al Rostamani Travel Winter Package', '<img src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20151231115651364.png" alt="" width="663" height="210" border="0" /><br /><br />Whether you''re planning the holiday season with loved ones, Select from a variety of packages designed<br />especially for you by Al Rostamani Travel. To know more please call <strong>800-ART (800 278)</strong> and experience a magical holiday.<br /><br />Austro-Bavarian City Highlights - 6 days<br />Vienna &ndash; Salzburg &ndash; Munich<br />Starting from AED 2,430 per person<br /><br />Package Inclusion:<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5 nights accommodation in 4* hotels<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Daily buffet-breakfast<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Arrival transfer from Vienna Airport to hotel in Vienna by private car<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; City tour Vienna including admission to Sch&ouml;nbrunn Palace<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Salzburg city tour<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Munich city tour<br /><br />&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *Train ticket (2nd class) Vienna &ndash; Salzburg - Munich<br /><br />Validity: 27 Nov 2015 &ndash; 22 Jan 2016', '20151207102717340', 'Yohan Aluthwala', '2015-12-31 14:09:39'),
(64, 'Sharaf DG - DSF Terms and Conditions', '<ul>\n<li>Double Air Miles is valid for spend of AED 3000 and above from 1st January to 1st February 2016</li>\n<li>Bonus Miles will be credited to member&rsquo;s&nbsp;account within 30 days after promotion ends</li>\n<li>Miles are not applicable on purchases of extended warranty products, items classified as impulse purchases or services purchased</li>\n<li>Not valid in conjunction with any other promotion/offer</li>\n<li>Sharaf DG standard Terms and Conditions will apply</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Careem&nbsp;Terms and Conditions<br /></strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Qualified members will receive an email with a promo code to be used on your Careem rides</li>\n<li>20% discount will be valid for 2 rides until Feb 29, 2016</li>\n<li>Maximum discount AED 30 per ride</li>\n<li>Members are eligible to collect Air Miles on spend</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Agoda Terms and Conditions</strong><br />\n<ul>\n<li>Valid for booking and stays until 31st May 2016</li>\n<li>Bookings must be made on www.agoda.com/airmiles</li>\n</ul>', '201601031433242', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2016-01-14 12:31:57');
