(66, 'Al Rostamani Travel & Holidays  -  Valentine Packages', 'Not sure how to spend Valentine''s this year? Check out great holiday packages and offers to treat your partner with <strong>Al Rostamani Travel &amp; Holidays <br /><br />Kempinski Resort &amp; Spa, Seychelles 4 nights/ 5 days</strong><br />Starting from *AED 4,125 per person on twin sharing.<br /><br /><strong>Package Inclusion:</strong><br />\n<ul>\n<li>04 nights accommodation in a Hill view room at the Kempinski resort &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Daily buffet-breakfast</li>\n<li>Arrival and departure transfer to/ from the hotel by private car</li>\n<li>Romantic Candle light Dinner 03 Course Menu&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;<br />Validity: 10 Feb 2016 &ndash; 20 Feb 2016 <br /><br />&nbsp;<br /><strong>Movenpick Resort Laem Yai Beach Samui 4 nights/ 5 days</strong><br />Starting from *AED 2,140 per person on twin sharing.<br /><br /><strong>Package Inclusion:</strong><br />\n<ul>\n<li>04 nights accommodation in a superior room at the Movenpick Resort Laem Yai Beach &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Daily buffet-breakfast</li>\n<li>Arrival and departure transfer to/ from the hotel by private car</li>\n<li>Full day Angthong National Marine Park with Snorkelling and Kayaking with lunch on SIC basis</li>\n<li>Romantic Dream Sunset Sailing Tour by traditional Jung boat cruise</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;<br />Validity: 12 Feb 2016 &ndash; 29 Feb 2016<br /><br /><br /><strong>The Oberoi Amarvilas, Agra 2 nights/ 3 days</strong><br />Starting from *AED 3,555 per person on twin sharing<br /><br /><strong>Package Inclusion:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>02 nights accommodation in a premier room with a view of the Taj Mahal at the Oberoi Amarvilas &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Daily buffet-breakfast</li>\n<li>Cocktail hour every evening from 6pm to 7pm</li>\n<li>Exclusive dinner at Pool Pavilion</li>\n<li>25% savings on spa therapies</li>\n<li>Transfers from nearest Railway Station or Airport (Agra).</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;<br />Validity: 12 Feb &ndash; 15 Feb 2016<br /><br /><br /><strong>Breezes Beach Club &amp; Spa, Zanzibar 3 nights/4days</strong><br />Starting from *AED 2,235 per person on twin sharing<br /><br /><strong>Package Inclusion:</strong><br />\n<ul>\n<li>03 nights accommodation in a Standard room &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Half board meal basis</li>\n<li>Return airport private transfers.</li>\n<li>Bottle of wine upon arrival (rephrase this as we cannot feature wine as a word)</li>\n<li>Flowers upon arrival</li>\n<li>Sundowners served in your room</li>\n<li>10% discount on a PADI diving course</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;<br />Validity: 01 Feb &ndash; 15 March 2016<br /><br />&nbsp;<br /><strong>Georgia 3 nights/4days</strong><br />Starting from *AED 1,590 per person on twin sharing<br /><br /><strong>Package Inclusion:</strong><br />\n<ul>\n<li>03 nights accommodation in a Standard room with guaranteed early check in on 1st day</li>\n<li>Daily breakfast</li>\n<li>Tbilisi city tour</li>\n<li>Sighnaghi tour (the city of love)</li>\n<li>Romantic lunch at the local restaurant in Signagi with beautiful panoramic view on the Alazani valley</li>\n<li>Transfer airport-hotel-airport</li>\n<li>Water on the transfers</li>\n</ul>\nValidity: 11 Feb &ndash; 15 Feb 2016<br /><br />&nbsp;<br /><strong>SHERATON MALDIVES FULL MOON RESORT AND SPA, Maldives 3 nights/4days</strong><br />Starting from *AED 3,395 per person on twin sharing<br /><br /><br /><strong>Package Inclusion:</strong><br /><br />\n<ul>\n<li>3 nights accommodation in a deluxe room</li>\n<li>Daily breakfast</li>\n<li>Return transfer by Speed Boat</li>\n<li>Airport assistance</li>\n<li>All Applicable Taxes</li>\n</ul>\nValidity: 11 Feb &ndash; 18 Feb 2016<br /><br />*Terms and conditions are applicable.<br /><br />&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Domestic Activities:</strong><br /><br />\n<ul>\n<li>Valentine Special at Fairmont Ajman - AED 900/ per night in a Deluxe sea view room based on double occupancy</li>\n<li>The package includes romantic room set up, in-room breakfast and late checkout at 3pm</li>\n<li>Upgrade to Junior Suite available for supplement of AED 300/&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Offer is valid for stay between February 12th - 16th, 2016</li>\n<li>This offer is subject to availability</li>\n</ul>\n<br /><strong>Monalisa Yacht Package</strong><br /><strong>Sellingprice&nbsp; 195 per person buffet dinner</strong><br /><br />Al Maha plays Cupid through the month of February&rdquo; Price: 1635 USD per room<br />Room on FB + Activities<br />Private suite deck dining with personal butler or Private dune picnic dinner under the&nbsp;stars<br /><br />\n<ul>\n<li>Bouquet of flowers</li>\n<li>Couple Massage in the suite</li>\n<li>Bottle of Champagne</li>\n<li>Chocolate-dipped strawberries, fruit platter and nuts</li>\n</ul>\n<br />Reserve a Valentine&rsquo;s Day Package for your other half and be enrolled in a raffle draw&nbsp;on 1st March 2016!&nbsp;To book call&nbsp;<strong>800 278 (ART)</strong>', '2016020113322631', 'Administrator', '2016-02-01 11:05:38'),
