(70, 'Sharaf DG - Exclusive Terms & Conditions ', '<ul>\n<li>This a Sharaf DG special promotion only for select DG Privilege members and can be availed by the holder of the card number specified on the email</li>\n<li>The offer is valid only for the GITEX period 30th March &ndash; 2nd April 2016</li>\n<li>Applicable only for redemptions at Sharaf DG stores. Not valid for redemptions at the GITEX venue</li>\n<li>DG Privilege members will need to validate each redemption request with personal data supplied to Air Miles at the time of payment. If the validation answers don&rsquo;t match profile information provided to Air Miles, the member will not be able to utilize the offer</li>\n</ul>', '2016032814144687', 'Ziyana Sharaz', '2016-03-30 05:57:16'),
