(74, 'Month of wellness', 'Throughout July, the Air Miles month of wellness, we will offer you exclusive wellness deals &ndash; from gym memberships to spa massages.\n<table border="0" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align="center" bgcolor="#f3f3f3">\n<table border="0" width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" bgcolor="#f3f3f3">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="stack-column" valign="middle" width="48%">\n<p>Stay fit with a 25% discount on a 1-month membership with <a href="http://www.classport.fit">Classport</a> &ndash; a trending app giving you access to unlimited fitness classes at different studios around Dubai. Use your exclusive promo code &ndash; <strong>AIRMILES16</strong> &ndash; to book today.</p>\n</td>\n<td class="stack-column" valign="middle" width="50%"><a href="http://www.classport.fit"><img class="fluid-20" src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20160630104037181.png" alt="Air Miles" width="100%" name="Cont_2" border="0" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="center">\n<table border="0" width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="stack-column" valign="middle" width="50%"><a href="http://www.poloclubdubai.com/en/leisure/the-spa.aspx"><img class="fluid-20" src="http://enews.airmilesme.com/am/mail-ex-imge/20160630104105181.png" alt="Air Miles" width="100%" name="Cont_4" border="0" /></a></td>\n<td class="stack-column" valign="middle" width="50%">\n<p>Unwind with a Buy-One-Get-One-Free spa treatment at the <a href="http://www.poloclubdubai.com/en/leisure/the-spa.aspx">Dubai Polo Club</a>, whether it&rsquo;s an aromatherapy facial, Balinese massage or antioxidant body scrub and wrap. To access this offer unlock Air Miles Monday, only available on the Air Miles ME mobile app.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="center" bgcolor="#f3f3f3">\n<table border="0" width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="